<p>According to Android documentation:</p>  <p>If your emulator must access the Internet through a proxy server, you can use the -http-proxy  option when starting the emulator, to set up the appropriate redirection. In this case, you specify proxy information in  in one of these formats:</p>  <pre><code>http://&lt;machineName&gt;:&lt;port&gt; </code></pre>  <p>or</p>  <pre><code>http://&lt;username&gt;:&lt;password&gt;@&lt;machineName&gt;:&lt;port&gt; </code></pre>  <p>What if my password contains the special caracter "@" ????</p>